                      <p>Taking into account the above Investor agrees to retain IMC to provide Investor with investment management services for the compensation specified in this Agreement. Subject to conditions, outlined above the Investor and IMC shall be legally bound by this Agreement in the same way as if it should and have been signed in a regular manner by the Parties and IMC seal were affixed thereto.</p>
                      
